race.description: Racing Mates Resilience Provincial Mdn Plate
race.comment: BLUE EYED BRIGID (7) back for her second campaign when launching late with a respectable second over 1300m at Newcastle. Racing like this trip will suit and Christian Reith retains the ride. Won't be a maiden for long. ATTESTOR (1) appreciated the drop in grade at the big odds when a gritty second over 1400m at Nowra in a Super Maiden. Will go back from the draw and be ridden for luck. LADY YARROW (4) consistent mare who drops in grade after sticking on well when fifth over 1400m at Warwick Farm. At her top now and no shock to see her win this at the good odds. RIDGEBACK (3) resumes for his second campaign. Struggled in the heavy going at both starts last time in and looks to have strengthened over the break. Given the two trials and finds a winnable race on his home track.
